outputs.output_descr: Advisory and technical assistance in assessing the institutional and individual needs of Prince Sultan Fund (PSF), developing its capacities, formulating development training programmes focusing mainly on leadership for young females, and exchanging best practices in the field.

project_descr: The project aims to achieve the Institutional capacities; Empowering the Saudi woman as an income-earner and a decision-maker;  Develop Leadership skills of 90 participants; and Identify and train 20 women as trainers
